I think you got to, you got to tackle the problems that are in front of them right away. And for instance, I think your timeline is a is a year, but you got to deliver pieces along the way. So one of the things that we've been working on, I've been there about a year. And early on, it was the customer lifetime value model.

00:17:26.800 --> 00:17:45.599
