00:47:41.600 --> 00:47:48.600
But maybe I want to just, as an aside, because it sounds like the issue with the R thing was something that I sometimes encounter,

00:47:49.600 --> 00:47:57.600
which is that the tidy data, the long version, is sometimes so unintuitive because it's such a machine-readable format than a human-readable format.

00:47:58.600 --> 00:48:08.600
